&nbsp;<hr />&nbsp;

<p>OK, fine, I hear you out there clamoring for my <a target="_blank"  href="https://bahamabucks.com/">Bahama Buck&#8217;s</a> shaved ice order, so here it is: Half Passion Fruit, Half Black Cherry with condensed milk and a little <a target="_blank"  href="https://www.seriouseats.com/chamoy-mexican-dried-fruit-and-hibiscus-sauce-7510202">chamoy</a> on top. You&#8217;re welcome.</p>

